node.contents: My application batch jobs hung without any errors in the logs. When the jobs are hung, there will be no database updates or inserts and I can see database blocks as well at the same time. Nothing happens in the system and everything seems stuck. See the complete thread dump I have taken during the issue time. Please help me to understand if this is the code problem or any external factors causing this hung in batch jobs. As a temporary workaround, I kill the database blocks or restart java wrapper service sometimes. It is really frustrating users many times. Thanks much in advance.
